Janet — Ask Janet Agent
The always-available operational analyst for GTM leadership. Design principle: output + insight agent. Reads data, returns contextual narrative answers grounded in TPS operating model rules. Tells you what a number means and what to do about it.
Category	Example Questions	Data Source
Pipeline and Deals	Which $1M+ deals stalled? What's my pipeline by close quarter?	D365 CRM + Workfront TD fields
Team and Capacity	Who's overloaded? What's our request queue depth?	Workfront requests + assignments
TD Coverage	Coverage gap in financial services? EAs on the right deals?	Workfront TD assignments + EA/SC criteria
Adoption and Hygiene	Team hygiene score? Who hasn't updated this week?	Workfront field completion + touchpoint logs
Actions and Priorities	What should I focus on this week? Which deals need attention?	NBA actions + operating model rules
Trends	This quarter vs. last? Touchpoint volume trending up?	Historical SharePoint archives
Phase 1 reads Friday Package SharePoint artifacts — a configuration exercise, not a development project. Phase 2 goes live-API when adoption proves out at 50+ questions/week. Same @mention, same questions. Only the data freshness improves.
