Friday GTM Briefing Package
Automated weekly delivery: one branded briefing deck plus two Excel workbooks per GTM vertical, every Friday at 5pm local. Zero human touch. Slack-first with SharePoint archive. The Slack message is the executive summary. Deck and Excels attached for drill-down. SharePoint files feed Janet's grounded knowledge.
Briefing deck (~10-12 slides):
Section	Content
Executive View	4 headline KPIs with week-over-week delta, AI-generated narrative summary
$1M+ Pipeline	Deal table by urgency — GNARR, Stage, TD, Tech Fit/Win/Risk, status delta. Stalled deals flagged.
Tech Driver Review	TD coverage matrix. Aging TDs. EA vs. SC alignment flags.
Request Health	Requests by status. Load balance heat map. Aging distribution.
Adoption and Hygiene	Field completion for all 9 TD fields. Touchpoint frequency. Team heat map.
Actions and Focus	Top 3-5 actions for next week with owner and due date.
Capacity recovery:
Activity	Hours Recovered
Weekly briefing packages	15-20+ hrs/week
Ad hoc leadership requests	5-10 hrs/week
Support channel answering	5-8 hrs/week
TD hygiene follow-up	2-4 hrs/week
